'''''Star Wars Insider'' 94''' is the second issue of the ''[[Star Wars Insider]]'' magazine to be published by [[Titan Magazines]]. It was available at [[Celebration IV]].

The special Diamond cover is the left half of a diptych with the second half being available on [[July 24]], [[2007]] on [[Star Wars Insider 95|''Star Wars Insider'' 95]].

